# Spec: 013-repo-ci-orchestrator
#
# CODEOWNERS: required-reviewer routing.
#
# Format: <path-glob> <@owner1> <@owner2>
# GitHub auto-requests owners as reviewers on PRs touching the matching
# paths.
#
# Ownership: @bartekus is the project maintainer. Forks should replace this
# handle (and the per-path entries below) with their own maintainers.
#
# Single-owner default for the template; downstream projects with
# multiple maintainers add ownership splits per path category.

# Default: every PR gets the maintainer as a reviewer.
*                                       @bartekus

# Spec spine + constitution: review these for contract drift.
/specs/                                 @bartekus
/standards/spec/                        @bartekus
/spec-spine.toml                        @bartekus

# CI + release plumbing: touching these affects every PR.
/.github/                               @bartekus
/Makefile                               @bartekus

# Application surface.
/apps/                                  @bartekus
/packages/                              @bartekus
